Map for M.I.A. Jailbreak, dated 25/09/2009.

Created by Zadori for M.I.A. Jailbreak.

This map contains a large vertical cell area centred within map games such as a race course, pool, playground, and soccer. A watch tower hugs the perimeter of each corner of the map. Inside is a medic and a kitchen with a physics button for dodgeball.
